{"tid":2326272,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"細田守新作 龍與雀班公主","createTime":"2020-12-15T08:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T12:33:22.000Z","uid":4618,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2d722521a43fad465d9f25db45ce402e3eefb96c","tid":2326272,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T08:16:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/studio_chizu/status/1338733139745640448?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstudio_chizu%2Fstatus%2F1338733139745640448%3Fs%3D21&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGC3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=bb92ba1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstudio_chizu%2Fstatus%2F1338733139745640448%3Fs%3D21&h=db868589\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/studio_chizu/status/1338733139745640448?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n    知名動畫導演 細田守，將推出全新動畫電影《龍與雀斑公主（暫譯，竜とそばかすの姫）》，預定於明（2021）年夏季在日本上映，官方並同步公開了首張概念美術圖。<br />\n<br />\n 這是過去曾執導有《夏日大作戰》、《狼的孩子雨和雪》、《怪物的孩子》等動畫電影的細田守，自 2018 年推出《未來的未來》後睽違三年的長篇動畫作品。本次的新作也同樣由他擔任原作並負責劇本，舞台是設定在集合了世界上超過 50 億人的巨大網路世界「U」，動畫製作公司為將於 2021 年迎接成立 10 周年的地圖工作室（スタジオ地図），關於作品的詳細情報還有待日後陸續公開。"},{"pid":"8d56386432c1902034c31883fb8b5786526b6b14","tid":2326272,"uid":10340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T08:21:36.000Z","msg":"好鐘意佢, 套套動畫都好warm"},{"pid":"3d29baf033d8eedb065709824e941db7cf0763c6","tid":2326272,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:13:37.000Z","msg":"還返個劇本畀奥寺佐渡子啦"},{"pid":"4410420ed17c0da1794d9275fe10ae609ad34906","tid":2326272,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:27:19.000Z","msg":"幾好奇佢跳出親情故事會玩到d咩花樣"},{"pid":"09e6a23763f8ae2c9036c5240379391aa92d209d","tid":2326272,"uid":365825,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:32:49.000Z","msg":"細田守好睇過宮崎駿，不服來辯"},{"pid":"aaee7a59ddd1b13e2a17a7e4611b6c5d3ee8beec","tid":2326272,"uid":10303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep